oai_dc:dc.dc:description: I want to say just a word or two about the kind of world in which we are living, how fast paced it is and some of the resulting obligations that we feel here at Oklahoma State University. I am sure land grant universities across this land feel the same obligations. They offer tremendous challenges as we look to the years ahead.
